column168: OUR VEHICLE BACKED INTO THE DOCK AT NORTHERN ILLINOIS METAL FINISHING- 716 CEDAR ST., ROCKFORD, ILLINOIS. ACID HAD STARTED TO LEAK OUT OF THE TRAILER. LIME WAS USED TO NEUTRALIZE THE SPILL. THE INNER PLASTIC LINER OF THE DRUM HAD CRACKED AND ALLOWED ACID TO LEAK OUT. AFTER THE LIME NEUTRALIZED THE A CID, THE VEHICLE WAS BROUGHT TO ELGIN. AMERICAN WASTE FO MAYWOOD, ILLINOIS CLEANED THE TRAILER AND PACKAGED THE WASTE INTO DRUMS. THESE DRUMS ARE LOAD ED ON A HAZARDOUS WASTE VEHICLE AND ARE BEING HELD AT OUR ELGIN TERMINAL, P ENDING THE ISSUANCE OF A EMERGENCY PERMIT BY THE E.P.A., SO THAT THE WASTE CAN BE PROPERLY DISPOSED OF.

column168: WHILE LOADING A TRAILER PARKED AT THE NORTH END LOADING AREA, A FORKLIFT OP ERATOR DROPPED A DRUM. THE FORKLIFT CONTINUED TO MOVE FORWARD AND RAMMED TH E DRUM CRUSHING IT. THE FRUM WAS BEING CARRIED WITH THE DOUBLE DRUM GRABBER . THE DRUM APPEARED TO BE SECURE BUT MAY HAVE BEEN CARRIED TOO HIGH ADDING TO THE ACCIDENT. THE DRUM RELEASED APPROXIMATELY 30 GALLONS ONTO THE LOADIN G DOCK. AN ESTIMATED TEN GALLONS OF THE GASOLINE/KEROSENE MIXTURE SPILLED D OWN THE LOADING DOCK ON TO THE DIRT WITH ONE GALLON REACHING THE FRENCH DRA IN. THE SPILL WAS IMMEDIATELY ABSORBED WITH CLAY AND THE CLAY, ALONG WITH T HE CONTAMINATED DIRT, WAS DRUMMED FOR DISPOSAL. THE MATERIAL IN THE FRENCH DRAIN WAS ALSO ABSORBED AND DRUMMED. AT NO TIME WERE ANY WATERWAYS IN JEOPA RDY. THE NATIONAL RESPONSE CENTER WAS INFROMED OF AN IGNITABLE HAZARDOUS WA STE SPILL (D001) AT 1:45 P.M. THE INCIDENT WAS REPORTED TO PETTY OFFICER O' BRIEN. THE MARYLAND D.E.R. WAS INFORMED IMMEDIATELY AFTER THE NRC. THE MATE RIAL REMAINING IN THE DRUM WAS TRANSFERRED TO ANOTHER DRUM AND DISPOSED OF AT:  FRONTIER CHEMICAL WASTE PROCESS, INC. NIAGRA FALLS, NY  (FUEL BLENDING ). THE EMPTY DRUM IS TO BE DISPOSED AT: GSX SERVICES, INC. PINEWOOD, SC (LA NDFILL) THE SPILL CLEANUP SOLIDS WILL GO TO : MARINE SHALE PROCESSORS AMELI A, LA (INCINERATOR)  1 DRUM, 600 LBS. THE ACCIDENT ITSELF MAY NOT HAVE BEEN PREVENTABLE, BUT THE EXTENT OF THE SPILL MAY HAVE BEEN LESSENED IF THE DRU MS HAD NOT BEEN CARRIED SO HIGH. PLEASE CONTACT ME IF YOU REQUIRE ADDITIONA
